{
  "stem": "14251.6",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And his hair had turned gray in a week and all these stories that we heard.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My mother tried to get laundry to him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My mother got two penciled notes from him, little scraps of paper that said, never worry about me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'll, I'll make it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then she saw him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She knew of a transport.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that same person told her that he was slated for that transport on August 4, 1943 to Auschwitz from, from the train station [NON-ENGLISH] which is in Zehlendorf, Berlin, actually in a very rural part, near a very-- part of an elegant part of town.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she ran there, as if she could, by some miracle, save him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But she was told by strangers, mind you, get away from here.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "People are running around with your ID picture because they presume that you may come forward.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And she saw in the distance, a small grouping of people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I think this whole transport only had 99 people on it because it was so late.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And saw a bunch of people in the background of another set of tracks, where all the cattle cars were.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But she didn't know, you know, him from somebody else at that distance and somehow had to leave there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The records showed in 1990-- it took this long to get records, mind you-- that he left Berlin on the 4th of August and he arrived in Auschwitz on the 5th of August.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There was none of this dawdling like the Eastern European trains.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I always figure maybe a half an hour of life left, small man, over 40, glasses, and undernourished.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Who has a need of this?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We know also-- we knew about the grandfather sooner.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
